reportData.title: SQL query for AMC_TRANSFER
reportData.contents: select top 100 origin_account_id, destination_account_id, asset_movement_gross_amt, asset_movement_net_amt, asset_movement_transfer_guid, asset_movement_instruction_guid, transfer_da, estimated_delivery_da from asset_movement_transfer as atr where asset_movement_type_cd = 'ACH' and origin_account_source_cd = 'BNK' and destination_account_source_cd = 'GNA' and transfer_status_cd = 'COMPLETED' and frequency_cd = 'ONE_TIME' and creation_user_identification_cd <> 'ACHTFRSC' and federal_tax_withhold_amt is  null and state_tax_withhold_amt is  null  order by creation_ts desc

SQL query

select distinct sub_acc.br_no
from PROD.SUB_ACCOUNT_12512 as sub_acc
where sub_acc.acct_id = 100

reportData.title: SQL query
reportData.contents:
select distinct rlt.RLTSHP_ID

from PROD.RLTSHP_13120 rlt
join PROD.ACCT_FUNC_GRP_DTL_13088 grp on rlt.ACCT_FUNC_GRP_ID = grp.ACCT_FUNC_GRP_ID
join PROD.SUB_ACCOUNT_12512 as sub_acc on sub_acc.ACCT_ID=grp.ACCT_ID

where sub_acc.acct_id in (100)
and sub_acc.br_no=68612
